import React from 'react'
import { Box, Center, GluestackUIProvider, Image, Text, VStack, View, } from '@gluestack-ui/themed'
import { config } from '@gluestack-ui/config'

export default function HomePage() {
  return (
    <GluestackUIProvider config={config}>
      <View backgroundColor='$primary0' flex={1}>
        {/* <Text color='$amber500' fontSize="3em" fontWeight="bold">NoteSketch</Text> */}
        <Center>
          <Image size="2xl" alignContent='center' justifyContent='center' source={require('../img/note.png')} marginTop={35} />
        </Center>

        <View p="$2" backgroundColor='$amber200'>
          <Box h="$80" justifyContent="center" ali>
            <VStack space="none" reversed={false}>
              <Box w="$20" h="$20" bg="$blue300" />
              <Box w="$20" h="$20" bg="$blue400" />
              <Box w="$20" h="$20" bg="$blue500" />
            </VStack>
          </Box>

        </View>


      </View>
    </GluestackUIProvider>
  )
}
